Name: VetIQ Healthy Centres Salmon & Mango Treats for Dogs, 70g
Description:
Introducing VetIQ Healthy Centres Salmon & Mango Treats for Dogs - the perfect balance of flavor and nutrition, specially crafted to keep your furry friend happy and healthy. Our delicious treats are packed with the goodness of real salmon and mouthwatering mango, making them irresistible to even the pickiest of pups.
VetIQ Healthy Centres Salmon & Mango Treats for Dogs Features:


Premium Ingredients: We use only the finest ingredients, including real salmon and mango, to create a delectable treat your dog will love.


Nutrient-Rich: These treats are a source of essential nutrients, including Omega-3 fatty acids from salmon, promoting healthy skin, a shiny coat, and overall well-being.


Grain-Free Goodness: Our treats are free from grains, making them an excellent choice for dogs with food sensitivities or allergies.


Supports Dental Health: Each treat is designed with a unique center that helps reduce plaque and tartar buildup, promoting excellent oral hygiene.


Made in the USA: We take pride in our commitment to quality. These treats are crafted in the USA, following strict quality and safety standards.


Resealable Bag: Our convenient resealable bag ensures that the treats stay fresh, maintaining their irresistible flavor.


Ingredients: 

Derivatives of Vegetable Origin, Meat & Animal Derivatives, Fish & Fish Derivatives (4% Salmon), Oils and Fats (1.4% Omega-3 fatty acids, 3.7% Omega-6 fatty acids), Coconut oil 4%, Fruit (0.5% Mango), Minerals.

Analytical Constituents:

Crude Protein 35.3%, Crude Fat 19.5%, Crude Ash 6.1%, Crude Fibre 4.0%, Moisture Content 10.7%, Calcium 0.7%, Phosphorus 0.8%.

Direction for Use:
VetIQ Healthy Centres Salmon & Mango Treats for Dogs are perfect for dogs of all sizes. Feed them as a tasty reward, training aid, or simply to show your furry companion some love. As a general guideline,

Recommended Amounts -الكمية الموصى بها




Up to 5 kg
